            "summary": "Liquidia Corporation, a biopharmaceutical firm traded on NASDAQ under the ticker symbol LQDA, shared news today regarding YUTREPIA\u2122 (treprostinil) inhalation powder. This medication, a prostacyclin analog, has obtained approval from the U.S. Food and Drug Administration (FDA) for adults battling pulmonary arterial hypertension (PAH) and pulmonary hypertension linked to interstitial lung disease (PH-ILD). The key focus of YUTREPIA is to enhance exercise capacity in affected individuals. Notably, this product is the inaugural prostacyclin dry-powder variant made possible through Liquidia's exclusive PRINT\u2122 technology. The methodology ensures consistent, unobstructed particles that aid in deep-lung administration. Additionally, the device used for YUTREPIA requires minimal inhalation effort, making it user-friendly.",
